  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  _comment: "The Leap XR Service Provider requires a reference to the camera you
    wish to use, ensure the Camera in the Leap XR Service Provider above is assigned.\n\nTo
    offset the tracking data, open up \"Advanced options\" in the Leap XR Service
    Provider and adjust the Device Offset Mode to either Manual or Transform. \n\n(Note
    : \"Transform\" Offset Mode will not work with temporal warping)."
  _isEditing: 0
